{"tid":249071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"10年內取代英文 普通話成國際語言","createTime":"2017-05-19T04:58:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T07:44:57.000Z","uid":91283,"like":10,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"95410cae7ed889c2b0f02e271394334c5a94a7e7","tid":249071,"uid":91283,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T04:58:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2004年2月28日<br />\n蘋果日報<br />\n<br />\n英語一直被視為國際語言，香港「番書仔」甚至以不諳華語為傲。不過這種想法已經過時，英國語言學專家格雷多指出，全球以英語為母語的人口正急劇下降，估計十年內普通話會取而代之，成為全球「必學」語言，而英語則淪為第二語言。 <br />\n格雷多在美國《科學》雜誌刊登最新研究，指出英語的地位，正隨着以英語為母語的人口而下降，由一九五○年全球有百分九人操英語，將會跌至二○五○年的百分五。預計在二○五○年底前，最多人說的母語依序為普通話、印度語和阿拉伯語。即使人們要學第二語言，也會先選普通話或阿拉伯語，而不是英語。<br />\n<br />\n微軟研究員中文撰報告 <br />\n目前的電腦、科學和航空交通指揮都以英語為主，但格雷多認為這只是專用英語，並指出一些航空事故，正是一些以英語為母語的人員，不能用正規英語溝通所致。 <br />\n他還發現使用中國語文是大勢所趨。以電腦業為例，微軟和英特爾都在中國聘請研究員，用中文撰寫研究報告，希望令對手無法看懂偷用。他說：「現在亞洲一些僱主已放眼到英語以外的語言。在未來十年，最新的『必學』語言將是普通話。」<br />\n<br />\n九成語言本世紀內消失 <br />\n格雷多相信未來的語言大趨勢，將會是朝多語言方向發展。人們在日常生活中將習慣使用兩種或以上語言溝通，但其中一種仍是英語。他也預言，在現存約六千種語言中，九成會在一個世紀內因少人使用而逐漸消失。<br />\n英國《獨立報》/美聯社"},{"pid":"a6d61869dc0a6b01740533aef444744b61dfca3c","tid":249071,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T04:59:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"254d0e97e17d8f0b7580ea67839d6a584b537646","tid":249071,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T04:59:42.000Z","msg":"bin c"},{"pid":"9991b41f604b9df30eaaa75578df2d5f89cd2fbf","tid":249071,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T05:00:33.000Z","msg":"突左3年,取代未 ?"},{"pid":"facd4d38131814ba63200d091f516c632fb021c1","tid":249071,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T05:02:49.000Z","msg":"國際認可生番語言"},{"pid":"b573ada0f86bd374d4598083c594ee51a8364d7b","tid":249071,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T05:10:34.000Z","msg":"當年就係呢啲笑話話到中文幾重要，搞到我地要讀咁多中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4dc44b78b4d049e8c064c8cc59ac9addc5b627f","tid":249071,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T05:13:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  香港十年變為二線城市    普通話十年變為國際語言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d80e51815c8cac9a71db78e8af3695ebdad88fe","tid":249071,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T05:20:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a207b6ef682bbb0047e970f854c30dbbb91a82","tid":249071,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T05:22:00.000Z","msg":"毒果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5e51afa4c14d0fc5c54fbbe827fa487c1fd4a6","tid":249071,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T05:23:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d4d196f3901b0d1a19ec697d0df19169316709b","tid":249071,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"